## Skill routing

# daily-stock-report — generate parameterized daily financial reports.
# Append the block below to your project or global CLAUDE.md.

When the user asks for a market update, daily stock report, or mentions
"美股"/"港股"/"A股"/"股票报告"/"market report", invoke /daily-stock-report.

Trigger examples:
- "给我一份今天的美股报告" → /daily-stock-report 美股
- "How did HK markets do today?" → /daily-stock-report 港股
- "每日股评 A股" → /daily-stock-report A股
- "Show me a report on AAPL and TSLA" → /daily-stock-report AAPL,TSLA
- "今天的市场报告" → /daily-stock-report (asks user which market)

### Cron usage

To get a daily report automatically, add a cron job in Claude Code:

```
/cron "0 18 * * 1-5" /daily-stock-report 美股
```

This runs the US stock report at 6 PM local time, Monday through Friday.
